  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Discover Floating Worlds</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vast array of randomly generated floating islands with unique biomes and resources. The environment constantly changes, offering new opportunities to gather materials and adapt to the unknown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/d563c77b3ed4f9348ac0f0e377a2cfc9.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/d563c77b3ed4f9348ac0f0e377a2cfc9.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/d563c77b3ed4f9348ac0f0e377a2cfc9.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Gather and Prosper</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Harvest essential resources like wood, stone, and rare ores to fuel your survival. From basic tools to powerful upgrades, every resource plays a role in your journey. The right materials could mean the difference between thriving or struggling to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/56dec53036698c844083d489fbddf3aa.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/56dec53036698c844083d489fbddf3aa.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/56dec53036698c844083d489fbddf3aa.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Build Your Fortress</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transform your main island into a thriving base! Construct buildings, upgrade your equipment, and establish a stronghold to protect yourself. Your base grows with you, becoming your greatest asset against the nightly threats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/255f5868499e7692e2397ee33d794ced.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/255f5868499e7692e2397ee33d794ced.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/255f5868499e7692e2397ee33d794ced.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Survive the Onslaught</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As night falls, waves of enemies swarm your island, threatening everything you've built. Arm yourself with powerful weapons and work together to repel the relentless attacks. Victory demands preparation and a sharp mind for survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/e48e588c9fbf255bbf9a1f7d7e2edc6e.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/e48e588c9fbf255bbf9a1f7d7e2edc6e.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/e48e588c9fbf255bbf9a1f7d7e2edc6e.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Enhance Your Power</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over 40 enhancement items that boost your stats and grant unique abilities. From faster movement to increased damage or health regeneration, these items stack to make you stronger as you progress. Each enhancement pushes you closer to conquering the Void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/cd363b278eb3b68dc0490418897c37b3.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/cd363b278eb3b68dc0490418897c37b3.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/cd363b278eb3b68dc0490418897c37b3.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Choose Your Champion of the Void</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of champions, each with unique abilities, strengths, and weaknesses. Whether you excel in magical attacks, ranged precision, or melee power, there's a character to match your survival style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/1b7c3422e398751278a83dc70ace7137.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/1b7c3422e398751278a83dc70ace7137.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/1b7c3422e398751278a83dc70ace7137.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Solo or Squad Survival</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive alone for the ultimate challenge, or team up with up to 4 other players. Share resources, cover each other's weaknesses, and face the dangers of the Void together. In this hostile world, teamwork is the key to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/eb0d496edc1eb80b0d92007d69341f81.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/eb0d496edc1eb80b0d92007d69341f81.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/eb0d496edc1eb80b0d92007d69341f81.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
