 src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/e48e588c9fbf255bbf9a1f7d7e2edc6e.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Enhance Your Power</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect over 40 enhancement items that boost your stats and grant unique abilities. From faster movement to increased damage or health regeneration, these items stack to make you stronger as you progress. Each enhancement pushes you closer to conquering the Void.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/cd363b278eb3b68dc0490418897c37b3.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/cd363b278eb3b68dc0490418897c37b3.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/cd363b278eb3b68dc0490418897c37b3.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Choose Your Champion of the Void</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of champions, each with unique abilities, strengths, and weaknesses. Whether you excel in magical attacks, ranged precision, or melee power, there's a character to match your survival style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/1b7c3422e398751278a83dc70ace7137.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/1b7c3422e398751278a83dc70ace7137.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/1b7c3422e398751278a83dc70ace7137.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Solo or Squad Survival</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive alone for the ultimate challenge, or team up with up to 4 other players. Share resources, cover each other's weaknesses, and face the dangers of the Void together. In this hostile world, teamwork is the key to survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/eb0d496edc1eb80b0d92007d69341f81.poster.avif?t=1766039973\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/eb0d496edc1eb80b0d92007d69341f81.webm?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3460920/extras/eb0d496edc1eb80b0d92007d69341f81.mp4?t=1766039973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
